Class PlayerEntity

java.lang.Object
com.university.persistance.entities.BaseEntity
com.university.persistance.entities.PlayerEntity
public class PlayerEntity extends BaseEntity
Represents a player in the game. Contains details like name, power points, current room, dungeon level, and status.
